2019-07-30	Jinshan Xiong	&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4398&quot; title=&quot;mdt_object_open_lock() may not flush conflicting handles&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4398&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4398&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; llite: do not cache write open lock for exec... &lt;br/&gt;
2019-07-30	Andreas Dilger	&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6202&quot; title=&quot;clean up ioctl handling&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6202&quot;&gt;LU-6202&lt;/a&gt; utils: remove obsolete l_ioctl2() wrapper &lt;br/&gt;
